title: Morrissey Reschedules U.S. Tour Dates | Pitchfork
text:
Morrissey Photo by Gabriel Olsen/FilmMagic 
Morrissey recently announced his first show of 2017 with the help of a Morrissey-referencing Donald Trump meme . He has now announced a few more shows, as fansite True to You points out. The five-date tour includes rescheduled Texas performances from the previously postponed leg of last year’s tour, as well as appearances at Mexico’s Roxy Festival and WWWY Festival in Santa Ana. See his full itinerary below.
